data.description: Located in the heart of Yucca Valley, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. Spread across 2,005 square feet on a generous 0.31-acre lot, a large 3 car garage, this residence is a true oasis of modern living. As you step into the home, be greeted by the abundance of natural light that fills the space, accentuating the high ceilings and creating an airy, inviting atmosphere. The upgraded appliances in the kitchen, complemented by sleek granite counters, make cooking a delightful experience. This residence seamlessly combines functionality with aesthetics, offering a haven for both relaxation and entertainment. The property boasts solar panels, a testament to its commitment to sustainable living, providing not only an eco-friendly touch but also contributing to long-term cost savings. The block wall privacy fencing ensures a sense of seclusion, allowing residents to enjoy the serene surroundings without compromising on privacy. Situated conveniently close to schools, this home is perfect for families seeking an easy and accessible lifestyle. Imagine the convenience of a short commute for students and the proximity to educational resources for families. Beyond the comforts of the home, Yucca Valley offers an array of local attractions and recreational events. Embrace the allure of the nearby natural wonders, with Joshua Tree National Park beckoning just a short drive away. Discover the vibrant local arts scene, explore quaint shops, and indulge in the diverse culinary experiences that Yucca Valley has to offer. This residence isn't just a home; it's an opportunity to embrace the unique lifestyle that Yucca Valley provides. Whether you're drawn to the tranquility of the natural surroundings, the convenience of nearby amenities, or the modern comforts within, this property is a testament to the perfect balance of suburban living and desert charm. Welcome home.
